        <abstract> 
<p>Asks AG not to send his rare specimens [of <hi rend="italic">Leucosmia</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Is glad of the notice about black pigs.</p>
            <p>Has great faith in Jeffries Wyman;</p>
            <p>thinks A. R. Wallace founds his speculation on a feeble basis.</p>
        </abstract>
